metadata.description: On this genesis issue of PUNKS Comic, follow our 16 PUNKS on their quest to capitalize on the metaverse revolution through enigmatic relics of crypto art history, The Lost Robbies, in what turns out to be a very wild ride. This Special Edition PUNKS Comic Issue #1 is 1 of only 58. The holder of this NFT will receive a PixelPass ahead of every Pixel Vault project drop. Each PixelPass is then redeemable for a free reserved mint of the corresponding drop. Holders of this NFT may access the full Special Edition PUNKS Comic Issue #1 here: https://www.mintgate.app/go/V5rdV7KARmdu/
metadata.name: PUNKS: The Hunt for the Lost Robbies (Special Edition)
